========================================================================
                      NOVA SENTINEL ONE-SHOT SCAN
========================================================================
Thank you for running the NovaSentinel One-Shot Scan!

This is a mock executable file generated for development, demonstration,
and evaluation purposes.

In a production environment, this binary is compiled as a native C#
single-file self-contained executable for Windows systems (x64) and
digitally signed. It runs once, gathers comprehensive system telemetry,
uploads a report, opens your browser to your live dashboard, and then
automatically cleans itself up.

One-Shot Capabilities:
----------------------
1. Instant system health and resource consumption diagnosis.
2. Direct connection to the report ingestion API.
3. No local installation or administrative privileges required.
4. Auto-launching live browser reporting.

